37a14ea6b1364ab4f5aec56b"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="zxx" dir="ltr"> <a href="https://t.co/r4VCV6oF15">pic.twitter.com/r4VCV6oF15</a></p> - Alessandro Paluzzi (@alex193a) <a href="https://twitter.com/alex193a/status/1665825542589775875?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 6 月 5 日</a></blockquote></div><p>现在说 Instagram 何时甚至是否会推出此功能还为时过早，但无风不起浪。 Meta 首席执行官马克扎克伯格<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/meta-is-working-on-ai-personas-for-instagram-messenger-and-whatsapp-223316961.html">在 2 月份表示</a>，该公司有一个团队正在为 Instagram、Messenger 和 WhatsApp 开发“人工智能角色”。 Paluzzi 也有良好的记录。就在<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/meta-verified-is-a-paid-verification-service-for-facebook-and-instagram-161632996.html">Meta 宣布它的</a>几周前，他在 Instagram 中<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/instagram-paid-verification-code-071024839.html">发现了付费验证系统的证据</a>。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/instagram-may-roll-out-its-own-ai-chatbot-in-the-near-future-200631539.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/instagram-may-roll-out-its-own-ai-chatbot-in-the-near-future-200631539.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 9fa43cd3-95ad-44ea-8af4-7de60b2aa53c</guid><dc:creator>克里斯霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Tue, 06 Jun 2023 20:06:31 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686082498</ingested><modified> 2023-06-06T20:15:00+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="1513" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-03/31a5a1f0-8803-11eb-b5f7-1238c4421ed2" width="2270"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media: